  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dda \u0d8b\u0daf\u0dca\u0db0\u0db8\u0db1\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 58.9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Inflation in June is 58.9 percent",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Headline inflation, measured by the annual point change in the National Consumer Price Index, rose to 58.9% in June 2022 from 45.3% in May 2022.",
        "There, the annual point inflation in the food category increased from 58.0% in May 2022 to 75.8% in June 2022, and the annual point inflation in the non-food category increased from 34.2% in May 2022 to 43.6% in June 2022."
      ],
